snippet.title: Jason Momoa says he HATES working with Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Welcome to our channel; in this video, You'll get to know Why Jason Mamoa Hates Working With Amber Heard.

We all know how fun and interesting Jason Momoa is. He's a person with a big heart, he's such a lovely and kind soul, to be honest, he's someone who would never think badly of anyone, whether he's friends with them or not, all he wants is for everyone else on this planet to be happy and satisfied. What we mean is that the 1.93 meters tall, well-built physique Hollywood celebrity is a prankster, and guess what, he never pulls a typical prank. Jason is one of the types that will test your patience and ultimately toy with it, so try to remain calm and patient with him.
